    <title>Assessor Roll CSV Collection</title><meta name="twitter:title" content="Assessor Roll CSV Collection"><meta property="og:title" content="Assessor Roll CSV Collection"><meta name="description" content="Contains five tables (MainData, NameAddr, SegMerge, Exemptions, and LegalDescr) that together comprise the primary export of Snohomish County Assessor’s Assessment Data. The MainData table reports assessment data for which there is only single occurrence for each property. Each of the other tables represent one to many relationships with the MainData table. A user can relate the other four tables to MainData using one of two fields, PropId or parcel_number, both of which are contained in each record extracted."><meta name="twitter:description" content="Contains five tables (MainData, NameAddr, SegMerge, Exemptions, and LegalDescr) that together comprise the primary export of Snohomish County Assessor’s Assessment Data. The MainData table reports assessment data for which there is only single occurrence for each property. Each of the other tables represent one to many relationships with the MainData table. A user can relate the other four tables to MainData using one of two fields, PropId or parcel_number, both of which are contained in each record extracted."><meta property="og:description" content="Contains five tables (MainData, NameAddr, SegMerge, Exemptions, and LegalDescr) that together comprise the primary export of Snohomish County Assessor’s Assessment Data. The MainData table reports assessment data for which there is only single occurrence for each property. Each of the other tables represent one to many relationships with the MainData table. A user can relate the other four tables to MainData using one of two fields, PropId or parcel_number, both of which are contained in each record extracted."><meta name="twitter:image" content="https://www.arcgis.com/sharing/rest/content/items/ee76dfa5905947cc9af1605a25cf216a/info/thumbnail/ago_downloaded.png?w=500"><meta property="og:image" content="https://www.arcgis.com/sharing/rest/content/items/ee76dfa5905947cc9af1605a25cf216a/info/thumbnail/ago_downloaded.png?w=500"><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary"><meta property="og:url" content="https://snohomish-county-open-data-portal-snoco-gis.hub.arcgis.com/datasets/ee76dfa5905947cc9af1605a25cf216a"><meta property="og:type" content="website">
