e.%20All%20persons%20accessing%20or%20otherwise%20using%20this%20Data%20assume%20all%20responsibility%20for%20use%20thereof%20and%20agree%20to%20hold%20Snohomish%20County%20harmless%20from%20and%20against%20any%20damages%2C%20loss%2C%20claim%20or%20liability%20arising%20out%20of%20any%20error%2C%20defect%20or%20omission%20contained%20within%20said%20Data.%20%20Washington%20State%20Law%2C%20RCW%2042.56.070(8)%20prohibits%20state%20and%20local%20agencies%20from%20providing%20access%20to%20lists%20of%20individuals%20intended%20for%20use%20for%20commercial%20purposes.%20A%20commercial%20purpose%20includes%20any%20business%20activity%20intended%20to%20generate%20profits.%20By%20proceeding%20and%20accessing%20this%20data%2C%20you%20agree%20and%20represent%20that%20you%20will%20not%20use%20any%20lists%20of%20individuals%2C%20or%20data%20from%20which%20such%20lists%20may%20be%20compiled%2C%20for%20any%20commercial%20purpose.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%7D%7D%2C%22width%22%3A12%7D%5D%7D%2C%7B%22cards%22%3A%5B%7B%22component%22%3A%7B%22name%22%3A%22markdown-card%22%2C%22settings%22%3A%7B%22schemaVersion%22%3A2.1%2C%22markdown%22%3A%22%3Ch3%20style%3D%5C%22text-align%3A%20center%3Btext-shadow%3A%201px%201px%20%23c8c9cc%3B%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EExplore%20Data%20Categories%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%22%7D%7D%2C%22width%22%3A12%2C%22showEditor%22%3Afalse%7D%5D%7D%2C%7B%22cards%22%3A%5B%7B%22component%22%3A%7B%22name%22%3A%22spacer-card%22%2C%22settings%22%3A%7B%22height%22%3A%2210%22%2C%22cardId%22%3A%22cw4lll83e%22%2C%22hideOnMobile%22%3Atrue%7D%7D%2C%22settings%22%3A%7B%22height%22%3A100%7D%2C%22width%22%3A12%7D%5D%7D%2C%7B%22cards%22%3A%5B%7B%22component%22%3A%7B%22name%22%3A%22markdown-card%22%2C%22settings%22%3A%7B%22cardId%22%3A%22caci3lcvj%22%2C%22schemaVersion%22%3A2.1%2C%22markdown%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22col-xs-12%20col-sm-6%20col-md-4%5C%22%3E%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22three-card%5C%22%3E%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Ccalcite-card%2